        Taxpayer 10-argument constructor. Calls the 10 mutators to initialise the attributes of a Taxpayer object with values that are set by the user.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the Taxpayer
        age - the age of the Taxpayer
        status - the marital status of the Taxpayer
        income - the income of the Taxpayer
        taxLiability - the amount of tax liability the Taxpayers pays
        USC - the amount of USC the Taxpayers pays
        taxCredits - the amount of tax Credits the Taxpayers pays
        PRSI - the amount of PRSI the Taxpayers pays
        netTax - the total net tax the Taxpayers pays
        totalDeductions - the total deductions from the Taxpayers income
